Premier. How far all that is! His dailyroute had to be closely established; I was one of the observers. Standing ata certain corner every day in the disguise of a vanilla-ice-cream vendor!Can you imagine that? Nothing came of our plans. They were thwarted by Azef,the great double agent."

I saw no point in prolonging my visit, but he produced a bottle ofcognac, and I accepted a drink, for I was beginning to tremble again.

